---
---
<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container about-grid">
    <div class="about-photo">
      <div class="photo-frame">🧑‍💻</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">About me</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">A little about how I got here</h2>
      <p class="about-text">
        I'm a software & web developer who enjoys the whole process —
        sketching an idea, wiring up the logic, and polishing the pixels
        until it feels right. I care about clean code, fast load times,
        and interfaces that don't feel like a chore to use.
      </p>
      <p class="about-text">
        When I'm not coding, I'm probably exploring new tools, tinkering
        with side projects, or hunting for the next thing to learn.
      </p>
      <div class="about-facts">
        <div class="fact"><strong>3+</strong><span>years coding</span></div>
        <div class="fact"><strong>15+</strong><span>projects shipped</span></div>
        <div class="fact"><strong>∞</strong><span>cups of coffee</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .photo-frame {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    border: 3px solid var(--color-ink);
    background: var(--color-pink);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-pop);
  }
  .about-text {
    color: #5c5470;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    max-width: 560px;
  }
  .about-facts {
    display: flex;
    gap: 36px;
    margin-top: 28px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .fact {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .fact strong {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--color-purple);
  }
  .fact span {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #8a8298;
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .photo-frame {
      max-width: 220px;
    }
  }
</style>
